OL,3,CHGV driver 'ignored' road closure and
OL,4,Cstruck council worker
OL,6,FCumberland Council is urging drivers
OL,7,Fto exercise caution and respect road
OL,8,Fclosure signs after a worker was
OL,9,Fstruck by an HGV wagon and injured.
OL,11,FThe authority said the HGV driver
OL,12,Fignored clearly marked road closure
OL,13,Fsigns and drove into the worksite at
OL,14,FSebergham Bridge, south of Carlisle.
OL,16,FThey have described it as a "reckless"
OL,17,Fact, which is "completely
OL,18,Funacceptable".
