OL,3,CHGV driver 'ignored' road closure and
OL,4,Cstruck council worker
OL,6,FThe council are reminding motorists
OL,7,Fthat road closures are essential to
OL,8,Fprotect everyone during road
OL,9,Fimprovement works, including drivers,
OL,10,Fpedestrians, cyclists, and council
OL,11,Fworkers.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Cumberland Council
OL,14,Fsaid: "To ensure the safety of its
OL,15,Fstaff, the council has implemented a
OL,16,Fcomprehensive three-part strategy to
OL,17,Fdeter abusive and reckless behaviour.
