OL,3,CHGV driver 'ignored' road closure and
OL,4,Cstruck council worker
OL,6,F"Large boards featuring images of
OL,7,Fhighway team members and their
OL,8,Ffamilies remind drivers of the human
OL,9,Fcost of unsafe actions, select team
OL,10,Fmembers now wear bodycams to record
OL,11,Fbreaches of road closures and abusive
OL,12,Fbehaviour, and mobile CCTV and signage
OL,13,Fcameras are deployed to monitor
OL,14,Froadwork areas, capturing any
OL,15,Fviolations or threatening acts.
