OL,3,CHGV driver 'ignored' road closure and
OL,4,Cstruck council worker
OL,6,F"The council emphasises that employees
OL,7,Fdeserve a safe working environment,
OL,8,Ffree from threats and intimidation,
OL,9,Fand warns that any form of abusive
OL,10,Fbehaviour, whether physical or verbal,
OL,11,Fwill result in appropriate legal
OL,12,Faction. The public are urged to
OL,13,Frespect all road closure measures and
OL,14,Ftreat staff with respect.
OL,16,F"The Highway Code prohibits driving
OL,17,Fthrough roadworks marked by cones or
OL,18,Fsignage. Motorists are reminded to
OL,19,Fobey temporary speed limits and to
OL,20,Flook for additional signs with
OL,21,Fspecific instructions.
